Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.86,0:06:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,零級 已經很好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Zero. Can't ask for much more than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.95,0:06:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧 最后一次肺功能檢查\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay. One last PFT.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.00,0:06:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.12,0:06:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不錯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.08,0:06:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,挺好的 就是今天了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Alright. Today's the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.13,0:06:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那我可以... - 就快了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- So, can I just-- - Almost.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.71,0:06:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你還得見一個人 然后就能出院了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just need you to see one more person, then you're good to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.47,0:06:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我的老天爺\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, for fuck's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.10,0:06:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你好嗎  - 挺好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- How are you doing? - Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.22,0:06:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,回答這么快就是不好的表現\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you say it that fast, it kind of implies you're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.64,0:06:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 再問我一遍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, ask me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.73,0:06:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,艾莉 你好嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How are you doing, Ellie?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.56,0:06:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我想想 這事很復雜 畢竟感覺這東西...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Give me a moment. It's really complicated 'cause, you know, feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.74,0:06:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.95,0:06:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托 我一直被困在這里 自從...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, come on, man, I've been stuck in here since...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.45,0:07:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯 我想他 他對我來說很重要 我既傷心又難過\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, I miss him. He meant a lot to me. So, yeah. Upset and sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.67,0:07:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,當然\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.38,0:07:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,但我好奇的是跨年夜的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I was actually wondering about New Year's Eve.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.88,0:07:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你們兩個在舞會上吵架了 那是你最后一次和他說話嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You two got into it at the dance. Was that the last time you spoke to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.84,0:07:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.85,0:07:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我回家時 他站在門廊上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When I got home, he was on the porch,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.43,0:07:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我該跟他聊聊的 但我沒有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and I should've talked to him, but I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.02,0:07:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你后悔嗎  - 當然后悔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Do you regret that? - Yeah, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.15,0:07:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,但你和一個人最后相處的時光\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But your final moment with someone 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.78,0:07:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不能定義你們整體的關系\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}doesn't define your whole time with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.82,0:07:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,道理是這個道理 但事實往往如此\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It shouldn't, but it often does.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.87,0:07:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,在我和喬爾相處的最后時光里 他曾說...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In my last moment with Joel, he said he
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.71,0:07:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,他對不起你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}wronged you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.92,0:07:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,可能很嚴重\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.05,0:07:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,他說他干什么了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What is it that he said that he did?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.26,0:07:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,問題就在這兒 他的話前后不搭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, that's the thing. It didn't really make sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.68,0:07:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,他說“我救了她”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He said, "I saved her."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.22,0:08:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,他救過我很多次\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He saved me a lot of times.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.39,0:08:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,對 換我也會這么想 但那不算“對不起”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, I would think so. But that's not wronging someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.06,0:08:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,真奇怪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.40,0:08:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道他什么意思\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No idea what he meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.11,0:08:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒覺得他對不起我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't feel wronged.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.66,0:08:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不管他說的是什么 真希望我能放過他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Man, I wish I could have let him off the hook for whatever it was he was talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.54,0:08:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,現在我只能放過自己了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I guess I'll have to let myself off the hook for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.13,0:08:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你做得很好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, you really are doing good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.26,0:08:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,見鬼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Shit, 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.51,0:08:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,如果人人都像你這么健康 我還怎么換取大麻和酒啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}if everyone were as healthy as you, what would I do for weed and booze?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.47,0:08:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不用擔心 這鎮上還有很多操蛋的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wouldn't worry, Gail, there's still a lot of fucked up people in this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.64,0:08:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,對 但你不是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah. But not you, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.04,0:09:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,(米勒)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.18,0:09:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,(喬爾 謝謝你做的一切)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.38,0:12:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,艾莉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ellie?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.63,0:12:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,媽的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.68,0:12:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我來了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, I'm coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.37,0:13:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我去醫院了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I went to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.29,0:13:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,他們什么時候讓你出院的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When'd they let you out?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.41,0:13:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- 30分鐘前 - 很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Thirty minutes ago. - Nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.17,0:13:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,他們讓我見蓋爾了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They made me talk to Gail.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.26,0:13:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我從來沒說...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I never said--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.30,0:13:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你來看了我那么多次 我早該說謝謝了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I should have said thank you for all those times you came to visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.26,0:13:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不用客氣 換我住院 你也會來看我的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's okay. You would have done the same for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.56,0:13:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- 對 也許不會那么頻繁 - 是啊 可能不會\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Yeah, maybe not as often. - Yeah, no, probably not.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.48,0:13:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我做了餅干給你吃\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I made you cookies.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.69,0:13:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,為什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just 'cause?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.98,0:13:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,算是一份和解禮吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is a peace offering.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.90,0:13:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,因為我要讓你生氣了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because I'm about to make you angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.12,0:13:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,在醫院里...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In the hospital,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.00,0:13:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你曾問過我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}when you asked me 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.46,0:14:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,那天的事...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}about that day,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.46,0:14:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我說我沒聽到任何有用的信息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I told you I didn't learn anything useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.22,0:14:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,其實我沒說實話\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That wasn't true.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.76,0:14:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道他們大部分人的名字 也知道他們是哪里來的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know most of their names, and I know where they're from.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.60,0:14:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你聽我說完\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please, just listen. 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.93,0:14:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- 醫生叫我不要讓你太激動 - 我不在乎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- The doctors told me not to upset you. - I don't give a fuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.56,0:14:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道我一旦說出他們在哪 你會拔掉輸液管\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I knew that if I told you where they were, you'd just start pulling your tubes out
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.61,0:14:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,爬也要爬過去找他們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and crawling on your hands and knees to get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.57,0:14:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我不在乎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't give a fuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.28,0:14:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你浪費了我們的時間 你讓他們逃走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You cost us time. You let them get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.70,0:14:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,首先\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}First of all,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.70,0:14:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,幾個星期以來 這鎮上一片狼藉 到處都是葬禮\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}this town was wreckage and funerals for weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.50,0:14:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,沒人會去追殺任何人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nobody was gonna go after anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.83,0:14:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我突然想到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And then it occurred to me, if you wanna find someone,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.13,0:14:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你想找一個人 而你只知道對方最終的目的地...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and the only thing you know about them is where they're gonna end up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.51,0:14:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,還不如讓對方先到了再說\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe let them get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.81,0:14:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我也愛他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I loved him too, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.06,0:15:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 我們先說名字\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, let's start with names.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.52,0:15:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,那個黑發男叫曼尼 另一個男的叫歐文\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The dark-haired guy was Manny. The other guy was Owen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.73,0:15:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,黑發女孩和光頭女孩里有一個叫諾拉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The girl with the dark hair and the bald one, one of them's named Nora. 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.44,0:15:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我不確定是哪個 - 那個扎辮子的女孩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I'm not sure which. - The girl with the braid?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.61,0:15:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,艾比\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Abby.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.45,0:15:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,艾比\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Abby.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.74,0:15:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,他們來自什么地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where are they from?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.87,0:16:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我在一個背包上看到了一塊布章\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I saw a patch on a backpack.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.92,0:16:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,黃色三角 有個狼頭...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yellow triangle, wolf's head,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.42,0:16:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,還有三個字母 WLF\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and the letters W-L-F.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.59,0:16:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我記得尤金給我講過 他還在火螢時的一個故事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And then, I remembered a story Eugene told me from back when he was a Firefly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.30,0:16:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,他說有些地區性小團體 都想對抗聯邦救災局\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He said that there were these small regional groups in the West all trying to fight FEDRA,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.43,0:16:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,還說他們沒有聯合起來真夠蠢的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and how stupid it was that they didn't just join together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.35,0:16:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,其中一個團體就是華盛頓解放陣線\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One of those groups was the Washington Liberation Front.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.44,0:16:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,來自西雅圖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Out of Seattle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.23,0:16:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,WLF 狼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}W-L-F. Wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.44,0:16:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,一群傻逼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fucking morons.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.78,0:16:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他有說這個團體有多小嗎  - 沒說\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Did he say how small they were? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.24,0:16:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不過 既然從那以后沒人提過他們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But seeing as how no one's ever mentioned them since,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.57,0:16:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我猜應該是我們能應付的小團體\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm guessing small enough for us to handle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.58,0:16:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,還有誰知道這事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who else knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.66,0:16:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,就我們倆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.71,0:16:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒打算在告訴你之前告訴任何人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wasn't gonna tell anyone before you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.81,0:17:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,現在怎么辦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.79,0:17:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.83,0:17:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我得考慮一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I gotta think about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.37,0:17:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,考慮什么 我們去干掉那些家伙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Think about what? Let's fucking get these guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.83,0:17:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,艾莉 事情沒那么簡單\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ellie, it ain't that simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.92,0:17:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,小鎮還在恢復中 你也一樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The town is still recovering. So are you. 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.76,0:17:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我們明白你的出發點 - 不 我們不明白\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- We get where you're coming from-- - No, we don't get where you're coming from. 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.09,0:17:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我不明白 如果死的人是你 喬爾早在天亮前就趕往西雅圖了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't get where you're coming from. If it had been you, Joel would be halfway to Seattle before the sun came up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.76,0:17:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,他那么做一定是為了救我的命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He'd be halfway to Seattle to save my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.06,0:17:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,可我們現在有傷亡 還不能走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But when we lost people, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.02,0:17:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,換他也會崩潰的 他會把一切責任攬到自己身上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It would just break him like it was his fault. 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.10,0:17:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我見過很多次了 別以為我不了解他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I saw that time and time again. And don't talk to me like I didn't know him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.06,0:17:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,他是我哥哥\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He was my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.99,0:18:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,聽著 我不是說你不該去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Listen, I'm not sayin' you shouldn't do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.70,0:18:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,但是既然要組隊 就得組一支像樣的隊伍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But if we're gonna put a posse together, we gotta do it right, 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.33,0:18:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,把這件事告訴瑪麗亞 沒錯 必須告訴她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}which means taking it to Maria. Yes, it's fuckin' necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.00,0:18:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,她會召開議會 通知全鎮\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's gonna want a council meeting, open it up to the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.92,0:18:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,每個想發聲的人都能發聲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Everyone who wants to get heard gets heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.13,0:18:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,但你會支持我們的 對吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you'll back us, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.42,0:18:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,當然\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Of course, I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.22,0:18:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,過來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.52,0:18:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,還有你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And you, 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.15,0:18:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你要是再有事瞞著我 就去最累的崗位上待一個月\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you hold out information on me again, you got rendering detail for a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.44,0:18:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.49,0:18:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,還有 艾莉...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ellie.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.41,0:18:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我們把死者埋在鎮南十英里的地方了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We buried our dead ten miles south of town.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.71,0:18:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以去看他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you want to visit him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.00,0:18:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,去西雅圖的時候再去吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When we're on our way to Seattle.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.68,0:19:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,(普吉特步道 植物園 西雅圖步道)
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.77,0:19:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.31,0:19:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,沒人跟來 很安全 繼續前進\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"No one following. All clear. Keep moving."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.07,0:19:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.19,0:20:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,等我們重新安頓好 我們會教你吹口哨的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Once we get resettled, I'll teach you to whistle.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.28,0:20:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你為什么不能告訴我目的地是哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why can't you tell me where we're going?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.16,0:20:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,因為我們還不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}'Cause we don't know yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.62,0:20:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我已經說了我們要去的原因\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've told you the reason we're going.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.75,0:20:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道 但她為什么不能保護我們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know, but why can't she just keep us safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.96,0:20:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,先知\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Prophet?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.46,0:20:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,她十年前就死了 康斯坦絲 我可不會指望她幫我們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's been dead ten years, Constance. I wouldn't count on her to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.55,0:20:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,但艾斯拉說先知是永生的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But Ezra said the Prophet is eternal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.30,0:20:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,從某種角度看沒錯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, she is, in a way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.68,0:20:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,但先知不是魔法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A prophet isn't magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.23,0:20:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,他們只是...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're just 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.27,0:20:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,能看到別人看不到的真相\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}people that see truths hidden from others
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.94,0:20:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,并且不計代價分享真相的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and share that truth, no matter what the cost.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.19,0:20:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我們的先知也是如此\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So it was with our Prophet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.57,0:20:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- 沒錯 - 沒錯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.24,0:20:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我們就是這樣讓她的精神永存的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's how we keep her spirit alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.53,0:20:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,遵循她的話語 服從她的教誨 同時保護自己的安全\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Follow her words, we obey her teachings, but we keep ourselves safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.41,0:20:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,那能給我一把錘子嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then, can I have a hammer?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.34,0:21:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.22,0:21:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,告訴我 你覺得更安全了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell me, you feel safer?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.01,0:21:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.60,0:21:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.64,0:21:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,要知道 我們現在給你的東西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Understand, what we're giving you now,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.89,0:21:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,會比錘子給你更多的安全感\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}will keep you far, far safer than a hammer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.85,0:21:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是出離\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.57,0:21:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,出離家鄉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}From home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.44,0:21:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,出離戰爭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}From war.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.83,0:21:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,找掩護 快\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Take cover! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.47,0:21:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,是惡魔嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Demons?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.60,0:21:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,是狼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wolves.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.15,0:22:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,很好 注意旋轉 再來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Alright. Good, but rotate. More.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.57,0:22:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,現在換右邊 只打右邊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, the right side. Just the right side.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.74,0:22:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,- 這邊傷害更大 - 我注意到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Come on, man, that side hurts more. - I noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.87,0:22:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- 來吧 - 好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Come on. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.41,0:22:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,用力點 堅持住 最后五拳\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Harder. Harder! Let's go! Last five.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.92,0:22:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好了 今天到此為止 - 好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- There it is, okay. Done for the day. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.88,0:22:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你覺得怎么樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, what'd you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.47,0:22:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,一個無所事事三個月的人能做成這樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, for someone who sat on their ass for three months, 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.51,0:22:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我覺得很驚喜 - 是嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I'm pleasantly surprised. - Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.39,0:22:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,平時做俯臥撐了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Push-ups?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.51,0:22:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,對 還在他們不注意時卷腹了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, and crunches when they weren't looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.51,0:22:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣就行了 再過幾周 你就能恢復原來的狀態\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, that'll do it. A few more weeks, and you'll be right back to where you were before.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.73,0:22:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.23,0:22:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,- 也就是你該有的水平的八成 - 隨便了 去你的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Which is 80% of where you should have been. - Whatever. Fuck you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.15,0:22:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,聽說你加入議會了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, I heard you're on the council now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.11,0:22:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,對\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.70,0:22:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,那你肯定知道接下來的會議\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, you know about the meeting coming up?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.79,0:22:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯 我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know about the meeting coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.25,0:23:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我能指望你嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can I count on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.21,0:23:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能討論即將開始的投票\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't discuss upcoming votes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.88,0:23:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- 搞什么 是我啊 - 我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Seriously? It's me. - I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.26,0:23:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,老兄 當時你也在場\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dude, you were there.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.05,0:23:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,這我也知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.43,0:23:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我得走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Gotta go.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.10,0:23:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,老天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.14,0:23:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,艾莉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ellie.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.94,0:23:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,聽完大家的意見 議會才能作決定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The council won't make up their mind until we hear people speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.98,0:23:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我給你一點建議\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, here's a little advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.11,0:23:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,把你的想法整理清楚 寫下來 明天念給大家聽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Organize your thoughts, write them down, and then read 'em out loud tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.11,0:23:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,- 知道了 因為我很蠢 - 因為你憤怒 艾莉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Okay, yeah, 'cause I'm stupid. - 'Cause you're angry, Ellie.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.03,0:23:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,沒人會投票給憤怒的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And no one's gonna vote for angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.84,0:23:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,...所以我一直說我們要多投資火雞\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Which is why I keep saying we need to invest more in turkeys 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.59,0:23:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,少投資雞\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and less in chickens.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.92,0:23:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,這就要說回我之前對玉米的看法了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And that brings me back to my earlier point about corn.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.39,0:23:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,有些人聽我這么說過 玉米不是最容易種植的作物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Corn, some of you have heard me say, is not the easiest crop to grow, 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.18,0:23:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,但它是生長最快的作物之一\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but it is among the fastest.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.31,0:24:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你們可以繪一張圖 把收成時間和所需資源以及難易度...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can plot a graph that shows ease and resources versus time to harvest and get a li--
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.94,0:24:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,斯考特 抱歉打斷你 不要偏題\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Scott, I'm sorry, but we gotta keep you on target here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.82,0:24:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,這是公開會議 章程上說...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But it's an open meeting. The bylaws say that--
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.11,0:24:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,或許我們應該回到 大家原本要討論的議程上來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe we should stick to what everyone else came here to discuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.82,0:24:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我對西雅圖的事沒意見\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't really have an opinion on the Seattle thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.33,0:24:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好 謝謝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.20,0:24:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,斯考特說完了 接下來是瑞秋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, that was Scott. Next is Rachel.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.75,0:24:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,喬爾對我們很多人來說非常重要...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, Joel meant so much to so many of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.00,0:24:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我聽不見 大聲點\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can't hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.84,0:24:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你能幫我抱著他嗎  - 好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Can you take him, please? - Yeah. 
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.38,0:24:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.77,0:24:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我說喬爾對我們很多人來說非常重要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I said that Joel meant so much to so many of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.90,0:24:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,但他并非唯一一個重要的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But he wasn't the only one.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.15,0:24:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,那天我失去了我妹妹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I lost my sister that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.98,0:24:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,這里很多人都埋葬了家人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A lot of people in here buried family.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.32,0:24:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,現在你們要派去16個頂尖成員\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And now, you wanna send, what, you're saying 16 of our best?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.57,0:25:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,他們不在的時候 如果掠奪者來了 誰去墻上抵御他們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, while they're gone, who's gonna be on the wall if Raiders come?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.33,0:25:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,墻還沒修好呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A wall that's barely mended.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.79,0:25:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,而且誰也不能保證 那16個人都能回來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And none of you up there can promise us that all 16 will come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.50,0:25:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我同情你們 湯米和艾莉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, my heart is with you, Tommy and Ellie.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.42,0:25:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,但我們傷亡慘重 現在出擊太早了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We are too hurt, and it is too soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.13,0:25:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你 瑞秋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you, Rachel.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.72,0:25:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,下一位是卡萊爾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Next is Carlisle.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.60,0:25:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我長話短說 畢竟這是個簡單的決定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll be quick. 'Cause this one's simple to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.77,0:25:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,有人來我們這里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}People came 
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.94,0:25:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,殺了喬爾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and killed Joel.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.90,0:25:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我們為什么不想復仇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, why wouldn't we wanna take our vengeance?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.20,0:25:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,因為我們不該那么做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, because we're not supposed to.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.74,0:25:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,寬恕他人 方能被人寬恕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Forgive and be forgiven.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.12,0:25:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,放下怨恨和仇恨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No grudges. No revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.25,0:25:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我都不是基督徒 可我一直覺得這么做很明智\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I'm not even a Christian. I've always seen the wisdom in that.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.71,0:25:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,這正是我們與掠奪者和殺人犯 不同的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's what separates us from the Raiders and the murderers.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.09,0:26:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我們懂得仁慈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Our capacity for mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.39,0:26:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,那些混蛋不配得到我們的仁慈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Those sons of bitches don't deserve our mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.52,0:26:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,當然不配 所以才叫仁慈啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, of course they don't deserve it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.89,0:26:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,去你的屁話\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's what makes it mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.23,0:26:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你能這么說 也不是什么好東西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, to hell with that. And to hell with you for saying it, Carlisle.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.23,0:26:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- 賽斯 坐下 - 不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Seth, sit down. - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.36,0:26:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你不在發言名單上 - 不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You're not on the list. - No!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.40,0:26:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我們到底在說什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What the hell are we all talking about here?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.61,0:26:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呦 太不公平了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.07,0:26:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我們要原諒每一個 騎在我們頭上拉屎的人嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What, we gotta forgive everybody when they show up and piss in our eye?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.16,0:26:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,他們闖進了我們家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They came into our house.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.54,0:26:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,抓走了我們的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They took one of ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.04,0:26:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My God, 
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.25,0:26:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,有人射殺了你們的兄弟 你們還想把門鎖拆了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}somebody shoots your brother, you wanna take the locks off your doors?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.63,0:26:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,幼稚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Grow up!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.59,0:26:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你們這些白癡 他們還會回來的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You idiots, they'll come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.55,0:26:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,因為我們沒讓他們付出代價\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They'll come back because we didn't make 'em pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.89,0:26:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,等他們回來時 一定帶著嘲笑的嘴臉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And when they come back, they'll be laughing.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.52,0:26:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,而你們都活該\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And you'll all deserve it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.52,0:26:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你們這群...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bunch of 
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.23,0:26:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,該死的受害者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}goddamn victims.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.16,0:27:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,(斯考特 瑞秋 卡萊爾 艾莉)
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.46,0:27:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,艾莉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ellie?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.35,0:27:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,“我通常不會準備發言稿”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I normally don't write things down
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.27,0:27:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,“因為我向來有話直說 不假思索”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}because I normally don't think before I talk,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.73,0:27:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,“這讓我惹上了不少麻煩”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}which has gotten me in trouble before, a lot,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.86,0:27:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,“讓我付出了無法挽回的代價”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and it's cost me in ways that sometimes couldn't be undone.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.95,0:27:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,“但我這次輸不起 因為我知道我的要求很過分”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I can't afford that right now, because I know what I'm asking is a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.24,0:27:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,“我要我們在最糟的時機”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm asking us to risk more people and resources,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.29,0:27:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,“拿更多的人力和資源去冒險”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and at the worst possible time.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.37,0:27:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,“我想告訴大家 我想要的并非復仇”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I want everyone to know, it's not because I want revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.46,0:27:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,“真的 這跟復仇無關”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not. It's not about revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.92,0:28:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,“我要的是 你們過去給予他人的東西”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What I want is what you used to give people.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.68,0:28:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,“我要正義”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.55,0:28:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,“因為除此之外 就只剩沉默與放棄了”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because it's either that, or we do nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.14,0:28:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,“而外面的人 也只會默默地放棄我們”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's what everyone else out there is going to do for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.52,0:28:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,“如果我或你們遭遇不幸”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nothing. A whole world of people who won't lift a finger
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.31,0:28:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,“全世界沒有人愿意動一動手指”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}if something bad happens to me or you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.69,0:28:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,“我們有專門的詞稱呼這種人”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We have a word for these people.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.32,0:28:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,“那就是‘陌生人’”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're called strangers.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.24,0:28:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,“我覺得我們之間不是陌生人”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I don't think that we're strangers to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.03,0:28:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,“我得知道我能依靠你們”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I want to know that I can count on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.58,0:28:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,“我發誓 如果有人傷害你們或你們愛的人”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I swear, if someone hurts any of you or the people you love, 
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.50,0:28:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,“你們也可以依靠我”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you can count on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.63,0:28:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,“這才是我們的凝聚力”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's what holds all this together.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.25,0:28:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,“不是聚餐 也不是跨年舞會”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not potluck dinners or New Year's Eve dances.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.17,0:28:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,“更不是一堵墻 因為那堵墻已經被撞破了”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Definitely not a wall, because that thing got busted through.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.14,0:28:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,“而杰克遜依然挺立”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But Jackson is still here.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.31,0:28:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,“我會接受議會的一切決議”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll accept whatever the council decides.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.48,0:28:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,“但我拜托你們”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I am asking you, please,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.81,0:28:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,“不惜一切代價伸張正義”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}do what it takes to see that justice is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.28,0:29:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,“不是為了我”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not for me. 
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.36,0:29:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,“甚至不是為了喬爾”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not even for Joel.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.74,0:29:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,“我拜托你們為我們大家這么做”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am asking you, please, do it for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.79,0:29:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.38,0:29:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,議會將就派遣16名成員前往西雅圖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The council will now vote on the proposal to send a party of 16 citizens to Seattle
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.43,0:29:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,尋找并處決殺害喬爾之人的提案 進行投票\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to find the people who killed Joel and execute them.
