Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.12,0:30:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,八票反對 三票贊成 提案被否決了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The vote is 8 to 3. The proposal is rejected.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.59,0:30:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,休庭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Adjourned.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.28,0:31:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,加油 九號球員\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Here we go, nine. Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.62,0:31:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好了 盯緊球  - 快\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Grab the ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.04,0:31:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好樣的 九號  - 加油 羅德尼 沖啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Attaboy, nine!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.04,0:31:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,- 該死 - 他沒事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.88,0:31:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我都不知道你是球迷\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I didn't know you were a fan.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.34,0:31:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,當然 我當年可買過老虎隊的季票呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hell, yeah! I had Tigers season tickets.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.47,0:31:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,這其實跟2003年的球隊差不多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This actually isn't that far off from the '03 squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.51,0:31:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,要喝啤酒嗎 我跟馬歇爾拿的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You want a beer? I get them from Marshall.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.53,0:31:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,今天開會時 我在人群中看到你了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I spotted you in the crowd at the meeting today.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.41,0:31:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,對\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.58,0:31:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我心想\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I thought to myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.95,0:32:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,“她過去幾周可能特別忙”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}she's probably been extra busy these last few weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.37,0:32:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,太殘忍了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Brutal.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.88,0:32:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我自己都該去看心理醫生 消化發生的一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I'm supposed to see a shrink myself, you know, to process it all, it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.13,0:32:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,可這里沒有別人了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm the only one here.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.76,0:32:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那你怎么辦  - 我是個酒鬼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- So, what do you do, then? - Oh, well, I'm an alcoholic.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.26,0:32:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,而且我盡可能地多抽大麻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I smoke as much weed as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.64,0:32:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,真是一場大災難\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know, complete fuckin' disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.27,0:32:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,但你來找我不是因為擔心我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you're not here 'cause you're worried about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.02,0:32:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,兩人出局了 各位 加油\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Two outs, guys, two outs. Look alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.65,0:32:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.52,0:32:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你能看到別人看不到的東西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You see things that others don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.15,0:32:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我擔心她會做傻事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm nervous she's gonna do somethin' stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.99,0:32:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- 怎么 你不相信她的發言  - 你相信嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What, you didn't believe her speech? - Did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.78,0:32:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,當然不信 她是個騙子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Course not. She's a liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.29,0:32:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,撒謊的人不一定是騙子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, there's a difference between lyin' and being a liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.75,0:32:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道 她就是騙子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, I know. And that one? Liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.04,0:32:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,她可能只跟一個人說過實話 而他已經...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There was maybe one person she told the truth to, and he's...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.76,0:32:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,但我們可以在這一點上各持己見\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But we can agree to disagree about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.22,0:33:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,問題是你很害怕 那我們談談吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What matters is you're afraid. So, let's talk about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.10,0:33:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不收錢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay. Free of charge.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.19,0:33:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是不想看她步喬爾的后塵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just don't want her to go down the same paths that Joel did.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.32,0:33:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,他滿口的正當理由\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Comin' up with justifications and such.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.82,0:33:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,其實只是在宣泄而已\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All he was really doin' was lashin' out.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.87,0:33:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你覺得她的行為可能是跟他學的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, you think she might have learned that behavior from him?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.54,0:33:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,其實后天教養的作用微乎其微 其余的都是天性\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Turns out nurture can only do this much. The rest is nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.55,0:33:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,就算她走上某條路 那也不是喬爾教她的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If she's on a path, it's not one that Joel put her on.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.47,0:33:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,不是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.09,0:33:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我覺得他們一開始就是并肩而行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think they were walking side by side from the very start.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.93,0:33:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,湯米 我明白\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tommy, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.06,0:33:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,現在她歸你管了 你想幫她避開麻煩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You inherited her, and you wanna keep her out of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.23,0:33:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,作為從業40年的心理醫生 我勸你一句\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Take it from a psychotherapist of 40 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.94,0:33:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,有些人...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Some people just...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.49,0:33:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,有些人無法拯救\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Some people just can't be saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.27,0:34:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是誰  - 迪娜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Who is it? - Dina.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.52,0:34:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 你好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.99,0:34:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我要睡了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm just going to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.86,0:34:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我不相信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, I don't think that is where you're going.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.50,0:34:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,就你一個人嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.37,0:34:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.84,0:35:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,進來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.68,0:35:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, Christ.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.81,0:35:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- 別勸我放棄 - 你以為我是來勸你的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Please don't try and talk me out of this. - You think that's why I'm here?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.89,0:35:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,說說你的計劃吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, what's your plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.19,0:35:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,去西雅圖殺死艾比\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go to Seattle and kill Abby.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.23,0:35:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,路線呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What route?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.94,0:35:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,西北方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Northwest.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.28,0:35:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,這里面都是槍嗎 有沒有醫療用品\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And is that all guns, or do you have medical supplies in there? No?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.99,0:35:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你最好別在你規劃好的西北路線上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, better not land weird on an ankle
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.58,0:35:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,崴了腳或發高燒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}or get a fever on your well-charted path "northwest."
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.08,0:35:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 我該怎么辦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, so what am I supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.34,0:35:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,遠離高速 避開城市或聚落\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stay off the highways. Steer clear of cities or settlements.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.63,0:35:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,第一階段是穿越國家森林\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}First stage is through the national forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.68,0:35:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,出來后 我們沿蛇河峽谷前進\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Once we're out, we follow the Snake River Canyon,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.01,0:35:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,- 然后穿越斯諾夸爾米山口 - 斯諾夸爾米\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- then break off through the Snoqualmie Pass. - Snoqualmie?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.98,0:35:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,對 斯諾夸爾米\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah. Snoqualmie.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.52,0:35:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,從東邊接近西雅圖 然后根據情況重新做評估\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Approach Seattle from the east, then reassess based on what we find.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.90,0:35:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,帶好糧食 輕裝上路 但要聰明\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Provisions. Travel light, but smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.65,0:36:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,拿厚外套當床墊 拿夾克當被子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Winter coats for beds, jackets for blankets.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.70,0:36:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,急救箱 電池和防熊噴霧都帶上 你要帶什么手槍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}First aid kits, batteries, bear spray. Now, handguns. What are you bringing?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.16,0:36:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,這是喬爾的嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is that Joel's?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.37,0:36:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你打算用這個殺死她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, that's what you're gonna kill her with?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.29,0:36:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,- 沒錯 - 那就留到那時候再用\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Fuckin' right. - Then, save it for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.38,0:36:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,它的速度很慢 后坐力特別強\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's slow and kicks like hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.17,0:36:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,真的嗎 你想轟掉你的屁股\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Really? Shoot your damn ass off?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.63,0:36:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,有人這么勸過我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've heard that before.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.26,0:36:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我們每人起碼得有一百發子彈 加上五十發步槍子彈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll want at least 100 shells apiece, plus 50 rifle rounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.93,0:36:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你想帶什么長槍都可以 只要有瞄準鏡就行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bring any long gun you want, as long as it's scoped.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.43,0:36:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,氯片 平底鍋 還有幫閃閃保持干燥的東西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Chlorine tablets, a pan, and something to keep Shimmer dry.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.31,0:36:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,- 只帶閃閃嗎  - 對\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Just Shimmer? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.98,0:36:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我們共騎一匹馬 減少資源\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We share a horse. Fewer resources.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.81,0:36:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,其他東西都跟你想的一樣 除了這個\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Everything else is what you'd figure, except this.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.78,0:36:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,靴子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Boots.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.74,0:36:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜歡這雙匡威 也尊重你一貫的風格\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Love the Converse. Respect your consistency.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.45,0:36:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,但你不能穿帆布鞋橫穿荒野\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you're not crossing open country in fuckin' Chucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.66,0:36:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我那么做過 - 不能穿帆布鞋 有問題嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I've done it before. - No Chucks. Questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.04,0:36:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,有一個 我們怎么弄到那么多東西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, one. How the fuck are we gonna get all of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.66,0:36:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我認識一個人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know a guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.83,0:36:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不是吧 你不會告訴杰西了吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, no. No, don't tell me you told Jesse, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.71,0:36:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,懷俄明隊長 沒有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Captain Wyoming? No.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.92,0:37:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜歡他 但他是個死守規矩的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I love the man, but he's a little uptight about rules and shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.84,0:37:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,把你要帶的衣服都穿上 口袋里裝滿子彈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wear all the clothes you're gonna bring, fill your pockets with ammo.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.93,0:37:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,其他東西必須裝進槍套或背包里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Everything else needs to fit inside a holster or your backpack.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.22,0:37:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我們凌晨三點在原來的東門見\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll meet by the old east gate, 3:00 a.m.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.89,0:37:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,凌晨三點\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}3:00 a.m.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.65,0:37:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.86,0:37:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.49,0:37:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,其實你可以直接問我的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know, you could have just asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.45,0:37:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道你愿意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, I actually didn't know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.74,0:37:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,現在你知道了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.95,0:38:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我換\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Trade.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.08,0:38:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,這把槍更好 跟我換\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's better. Trade.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.31,0:38:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么把它弄出來的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How'd you get her out?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.43,0:38:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,珍寧在馬廄值夜班 她理解我們想做的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Jeanine's night watch at the stables. She's sympathetic to our cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.69,0:38:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我們想做的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Our cause"?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.06,0:38:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,是你在議會上說“我們”的 不是我說的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're the one that gave the "us" speech, not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.61,0:38:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,馬鞍袋里都是我偷藏的東西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Saddlebags are filled with stuff I had squirreled away.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.40,0:38:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,能吃兩周的硬面包 繃帶 酒精 藥物和電池\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Two weeks' worth of hardtack, bandages, alcohol, meds, batteries.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.99,0:38:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我想跟你們一起去 但我在跨年夜被友軍誤傷了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd come with you, but I caught some friendly fire on New Year's Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.49,0:38:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你確定是友軍嗎  - 天啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You sure it was friendly? - Jesus Christ.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.16,0:39:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,在巡邏隊經過之前 你們只有十分鐘 快走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We got ten minutes before a patrol comes by. Let's get you going.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.07,0:40:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,(喬爾米勒)
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.19,0:42:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 字母F\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, so...F.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.07,0:43:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,字母F 佛...佛利伍麥克樂團\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}F. Fleetwood Mac. 
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.91,0:43:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不對 - 什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Nope. - What? 
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.29,0:43:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,什么叫不對 這是我的看法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do you mean, "no"? It's my opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.00,0:43:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你的看法是錯的 因為弗蘭克扎帕真的存在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, well, your opinion is wrong because Frank Zappa exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.00,0:43:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 字母G\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, so, G.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.21,0:43:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- 綠日樂隊 - 不 你錯了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Green Day. - No, you're wrong. It's Guns N' Roses.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.64,0:43:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,奧茲奧斯朋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ozzy Osbourne.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.14,0:43:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,很好 分數加倍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nice! Double points.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.39,0:43:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,L M N O P\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, L-M-N-O, P.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.94,0:43:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你真要讓我猜完所有字母嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you seriously gonna make me do the entire alphabet?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.98,0:43:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不用 我很靈活的 讓我想想 換個新話題...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We don't have to. I'm incredibly flexible. Lemme see, new topic.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.15,0:43:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- 沉默也行 - 有了 你殺的第一個人是誰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Or silence. - Got one. First person you killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.82,0:43:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊 真的嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Jesus, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.24,0:43:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,對 有趣的童年故事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, fun stories of childhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.20,0:43:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,第一個人死得太離譜 但我可以跟你說說第二個\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, well, the first one's too fucked up, but I can tell you the second one.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.96,0:43:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,沒問題\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.75,0:43:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,那是我和喬爾來杰克遜之前的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was a little before Joel and I got to Jackson.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.25,0:44:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,在堪薩斯城 他被一個沒比我大幾歲的孩子突襲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In Kansas City, he got jumped by this kid, maybe just a couple years older than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.84,0:44:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我從后面接近他 舉起槍 然后...就這樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I came up behind him, raised my gun and, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.81,0:44:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 艾莉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sorry, Ellie.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.85,0:44:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,有意思 殺人的是我 你卻替我難過\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Interesting. I shoot a guy, and you feel sorry for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.94,0:44:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是這么忠誠\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm just loyal like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.69,0:44:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你看到露巖或有遮蔽的地方 記得告訴我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let me know if you see any outcroppings or spots with cover.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.74,0:44:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,為什么 天氣挺好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why? It looks okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.79,0:44:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我的天 雨來得真快 你怎么知道會這樣的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Holy shit, that came on fast. How the fuck did you know that was gonna happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.96,0:44:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我是女巫 - 顯然是這樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I'm a witch. - Clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.44,0:45:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.95,0:45:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Night.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.55,0:45:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不過 我還有個蠢問題\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, but I have a stupid question.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.06,0:45:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,和跨年夜有關\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's about New Year's Eve, and, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.52,0:45:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,那個吻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.07,0:45:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,好 也沒什么 你當時嗑嗨了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay. I mean, whatever, you were super high.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.53,0:45:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,而你醉了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And you were drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.11,0:45:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,對 所以那不能代表什么 你是想問這個吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Right, so it doesn't mean anything, if that's what you're asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.95,0:45:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不 這個我知道 我想問的是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, I know that. My question is,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.71,0:45:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你會給那個吻打幾分\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}how would you rate it?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.96,0:46:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- 一到十分  - 不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Scale of one to ten. - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.04,0:46:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托 你以前吻過女孩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on. You've kissed girls before. 
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.42,0:46:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你是同性戀 而我不是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're gay, I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.59,0:46:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是好奇 我想知道我厲不厲害\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm just curious. I wanna know if I'm any good at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.26,0:46:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,一到十分\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One to ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.68,0:46:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 六分\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, fine. Six.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.39,0:46:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- 去你的 六分  - 這算不錯了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Fuck you, "six." - That's not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.11,0:46:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,真是爛透了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That sucks!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.86,0:46:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.32,0:46:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,鄭重聲明一下 我不相信你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For the record, I don't believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.24,0:46:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你非要問 我就答了 對不起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, you asked, and I told you. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.45,0:46:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以回去找杰西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can go back to Jesse.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.54,0:46:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我已經找了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I already did.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.79,0:46:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,那就行了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, there you have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.09,0:46:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,他有沒有給你一種悲傷的感覺\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Does he ever strike you as sad?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.10,0:46:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,杰西嗎 有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Jesse? Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.31,0:46:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,他跟你說過原因嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Has he ever told you why?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.27,0:47:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.52,0:47:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,但我覺得他內心深處就是悲傷的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I think deep inside, that's just how he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.74,0:47:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- 至少我希望是這樣 - 為什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- At least, I hope that's why. - Why would you hope that?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.66,0:47:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,因為如果不是的話...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, because if it's not that,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.33,0:47:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是我的問題了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}then it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.51,0:47:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.47,0:47:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Night.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.40,0:47:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,艾莉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ellie?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.82,0:47:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,當時我沒那么嗨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wasn't that high.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.91,0:47:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,(植物園 西雅圖步道)
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.71,0:48:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,還有多遠\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How much further?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.50,0:48:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,很近了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Close.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.42,0:48:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,大約十英里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe ten miles?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.67,0:48:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,理論上 我們會從城北五號公路附近穿出去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In theory, we'll come out near Highway Five, just north of the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.65,0:48:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,他死前正在逃跑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He was running away.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.20,0:48:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,這是什么符號\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's that symbol?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.20,0:48:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道 我也是第一次見\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know, I've never seen it before.
