Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.68,0:48:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,迪娜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dina?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.77,0:49:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你沒事吧  - 那邊...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You okay? - It's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.12,0:50:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你沒事吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Doing okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.67,0:50:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起 我從沒有過這種反應\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, I'm sorry, it's just that's never happened before.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.71,0:50:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,- 可能是氣味太重 - 而且慘不忍睹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I think it was the smell. - It wasn't easy to look at either.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.22,0:50:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,如果這是他們干的...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If this was fucking them,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.26,0:50:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,如果艾比和她的人能對人干出這種事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}if Abby and her crew did this to people,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.85,0:50:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,能殺害孩子...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.98,0:50:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,對\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.03,0:50:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.68,0:51:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,已經很接近了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're close now.
