Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.92,0:51:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,好安靜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.51,0:51:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,對 過于安靜了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah. Too quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.30,0:51:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,柯蒂斯還是毒蛇的臺詞\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Curtis or Viper?
