Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.42,0:52:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,該死的西雅圖 真漂亮\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fucking Seattle. Pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.89,0:52:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,而且也沒人對我們開槍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Plus, no one's shooting at us.
